Rapper Victor Ncha Odu aka Vic O has professed love for billionaire heiress, Florence Otedola aka DJ Cuppy. The internet sensation recently joined the list of men wooing the “Gelatto” crooner in a video shared on his Twitter handle as a response to the latter’s tweet. The disc jockey, following reports of Rihanna’s pregnancy, lamented she is still single. “Rihanna is pregnant and I’m still single,” Cuppy tweeted. Reacting to DJ Cuppy’s lamentation, Vic O in a video informed her that he’s available. - Advertisement - He noted Cuppy should waste no time in contacting him if she likes him too as he’s very much single for her.   M.I. Abaga to quit bachelorhood in 2022?     Olamide hints of fresh collaboration with Wande Coal     I am frantically praying for a daughter-in-law, says…   Vic O said: “Hey DJ Cuppy. I read your comment that you posted saying, ‘Rihanna has taken in and you haven’t’. Babe, I dey here now. I full ground. “Hmmm….don’t you like my style? Don’t you like my lips? Don’t you like my cool colour? Come on DJ Cuppy, let’s make it happen. “My doors are open. I’m very much single for you. If you like me too, waste no time. Just hit the button.” He captioned the video: “Short note to you my queen-to-be. @cuppymusic. I’m very much available for you babe……. You Gon’ love ma style…I’m a cool dude you know. “You know I’ve been in love with ya for a long time… And if we’ve met before now I will have proposed to you without wasting time…” Cuppy has also reacted to Vic O’s message. She shared the video on her Insta story with the caption: “Best TikTok of the day.”